OL,6,FAttempts to contact the owners of
OL,7,FLegacy Independent Funeral Directors
OL,8,Fas part of formal steps to dissolve
OL,9,Fthe business have so far failed, a
OL,10,Fcourt has heard.
OL,12,FThe Hull-based firm is at the centre
OL,13,Fof a major police investigation over
OL,14,Fconcerns about its care for the
OL,15,Fdeceased.
OL,17,FTwo people have been arrested on
OL,18,Fsuspicion of fraud and preventing a
OL,19,Flawful and decent burial and remain on
OL,20,Fbail.
