OL,3,CCouncil unable to serve winding up
OL,4,Corder on funeral firm, court hears
OL,6,FPaul Thompson, representing Hull City
OL,7,FCouncil, said: "In essence there's no
OL,8,Fone from the company managing the
OL,9,Fbusiness affairs on that basis to
OL,10,Fserve a winding-up petition."
OL,12,FNo-one from the company was present at
OL,13,Fthe hearing.
OL,15,FThe case was adjourned for three weeks
OL,16,Fto give the authority additional time
OL,17,Fto try to serve the petition.
