OL,3,CCouncil unable to serve winding up
OL,4,Corder on funeral firm, court hears
OL,6,FLegacy has not been in operation since
OL,7,FHumberside Police began an
OL,8,Finvestigation into what they called a
OL,9,F"truly horrific incident" on 6 March.
OL,11,FOn Thursday, police said it was not
OL,12,Fpossible to identify any of the
OL,13,Fcremated ashes because "the DNA will
OL,14,Fhave been broken down and degraded"
OL,15,Fdue to the high temperature during the
OL,16,Fcremation process.
OL,18,FPolice and the council are now in
OL,19,Fcontrol of the company's premises.
