OL,3,CCouncil unable to serve winding up
OL,4,Corder on funeral firm, court hears
OL,6,FIn a statement on 27 March the council
OL,7,Fsaid it had last year obtained a
OL,8,Fcounty court judgement in relation to
OL,9,Funpaid fees and charges, including
OL,10,Fcremation fees, amounting to more than
OL,11,F#50,000.
OL,13,FA spokesperson added: "A payment
OL,14,Farrangement was put in place, with the
OL,15,Flast payment being made to the Council
OL,16,Fon 2 February 2024. The remaining debt
OL,17,Fis now #40,938.08.
OL,19,F"We are exploring options to recoup
OL,20,Fthat sum, and have issued a petition
OL,21,Fto wind up the company."
